{"tid":1039003,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[試伏]Starbucks 櫻花系列俾狗飲","createTime":"2019-02-27T06:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T10:04:35.000Z","uid":232382,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f16e232ba6df8c1e4cc53fedcd7be1e17f6c0ae5","tid":1039003,"uid":232382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T06:17:57.000Z","msg":"「紅豆忌廉花見星冰樂」改到個名咁grand, 實際上只係紅豆冰！！！！！<br />\n賣$45嘅紅豆冰！！！<br />\n連店員落單嗰陣都係叫紅豆冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要係難飲嘅紅豆冰！！！！<br />\n紅豆應該美心嗰隻紅豆！一樣味！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nExpectation:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZLqAM0Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZLqAM0Q.png&h=8ef831be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nReality:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PcX3VUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPcX3VUk.png&h=36a08eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n宣傳圖片上粉紅色奶係假的！實際上你只會得到一杯白色豆奶，底有少少紅豆咁！<br />\n<br />\n茶記都好飲過佢呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a7e21d1168074b5820b5498480bafcdade0659","tid":1039003,"uid":191633,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T06:20:20.000Z","msg":"難得清做咗白老鼠唔洗我冒險試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />starfucks啲凍嘅抹茶無味嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e82c616cbf22eca9a3985e8ffba58f4338e3b6","tid":1039003,"uid":232382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12a7e21d1168074b5820b5498480bafcdade0659","tid":1039003,"uid":191633,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T06:20:20.000Z","msg":"難得清做咗白老鼠唔洗我冒險試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />starfucks啲凍嘅抹茶無味嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif